# TaxBackwards.ca — Complete Project Summary

## Project Overview
A Canadian reverse sales tax calculator web tool targeting bookkeepers, freelancers, sole proprietors, and small business owners. Allows users to extract pre-tax net amounts and claimable Input Tax Credits (ITCs) from gross transaction totals across all 13 Canadian provinces. Domain concept: TaxBackwards.ca

Core Stack: Vanilla HTML/CSS/JS, GitHub, Cloudflare Pages, Plausible Analytics, GitHub Actions — all free. Operational overhead scales to zero outside domain registration (~$12/year CAD).

