- Configure SRI hashing on any CDN-loaded scripts
- Set up Google Alert for GST HST rate change
Launch gate: working calculator live on domain

### Stage 2 — Content Expansion for AdSense Eligibility
Timeline: Week 3–8
- Build /provinces/ontario/ informational sub-page
