Launch gate: minimum two provincial sub-pages live, affiliate application submitted

### Stage 3 — Full Provincial Rollout and Monetization
Timeline: Month 3–6
- Add BC, Alberta, Nova Scotia to taxRates.js and build corresponding sub-pages
- Build /rate-history/ section with historical rate documentation
- Apply to QuickBooks Canada affiliate program
- Introduce manually placed static AdSense ad units in fixed sidebar positions if traffic warrants — do not use Auto Ads
- If AdSense added, implement geofenced CMP banner for Quebec visitors via Cloudflare Workers
- Add Status Card / First Nations Section 87 exemption toggle
- Build dedicated /status-card-exemptions/ sub-page for long-tail SEO
- Add Apportionment Percentage Slider for freelancer partial expense claiming
- Implement URL parameter sanitization before this feature if shareable URLs are added
- Rotate Discord webhook if used, document rotation procedure
